* does
	* reads in Nigeria, WAVE 1 (2010-2011) POST PLANTING, NIGERIA SECT 11C
	* creates binaries for pesticide and herbicide use
	* outputs clean data file ready for combination with wave 1 plot data

* assumes
	* customsave.ado
	* mdesc.ado
	
